ter\nmass fractions than objects with young stellar populations, such as isolated\ndwarfs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Aug 2020 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Jan 2021 17:26:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-11"}
