TCHA, but the improvement is limited. Conversely, generating more complex\nCAPTCHAs may cost more resources and reduce the availability of CAPTCHAs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Aug 2020 14:57:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-27"}
