axy, observed at the center of local\nclusters. According to our data, all galaxies in the core of XDCPJ0044.0-2033\ncould form a BCG of Mstar ~ 10^{12} Msun hosting a BH of 2 x 10^{8}-10^{9}Msun,\nin a time scale of the order of 2.5 Gyrs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Aug 2020 08:47:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-28"}
